    "viewAll": "View All",
    "aboutTitle": "What is Souk ElKanto, exactly?",
    "aboutNeighbors": "Your neighbors, not strangers",
    "aboutNeighborsBody": "Every seller and buyer is verified. You know who you're talking to: your neighbor, not a faceless account.",
    "aboutBroker": "A broker, never a bank",
    "aboutBrokerBody": "No money moves through the platform. Post, offer, meet. The deal stays between you and your neighbor.",
    "aboutWhatsApp": "Works like WhatsApp",
    "aboutWhatsAppBody": "Share any listing to WhatsApp with one tap. Communicate the way you already do.",
    "heritageTitle": "The Roots of ElKanto",
    "heritageBody": "The name 'ElKanto' is drawn from the original Souk ElKanto in Port Said — a traditional market that rose in the late 19th century with the opening of the Suez Canal. It was a bustling hub for trading goods from passing ships, and became an iconic symbol of Port Said's heritage. Souk ElKanto digital revives that spirit: trade between neighbors, trust before profit."
  },
